The head of the ISC (Superior Institution of Control of Public Finance) said: "The control of pseudo self-employment (in Czech " Švarc system ") failed because of politicians.
In the area of public procurement, the Czech Republic has competent inspectors and quality legislation, but it is lagging behind in its implementation.
