We decided to use the marketing potential of the end of the Mayan calendar announced for December 21 at 11:10 a.m.
The day before, on 20 December, three concerts will take place simultaneously in Prague, Brno and Ostrava.
They will end almost at the end of the Mayan calendar on the island of Kiribati in the Pacific Ocean, over a 12-hour time zone ahead of us.
Who had that idea?
