It will be sung simultaneously by all the performers in all three concerts.
The anthems will also join at some point as part of a very unique live broadcast on Czech television.
The lyrics of this song were written by Tom+ Hanák who also holds the leading role of Jesus in the clip, Xindl X sings there as well...
