It's like the Eurovision contest.
"What score did you give to the best fish in the Thor-Juergen Mountains?"
"Here are our points, Havard."
We hear laughter and applause.
A man falls from his chair, perhaps because of the abuse of aquavit.
Or maybe it's because of the fish emanations.
Mexico's Enrique Pena Nieto has a difficult start.
